set responsive design.

screen = mobile, tablet, monitor, leptop

breakpoints 
max-width    =  576px   = mobile screen 
min-width    =  576px   = large mobile screen 
min-width    =  768px   = tablet screen (medium)
min-width    =  992px   = large 
min-width    =  1200    = extra large 
min-width    =  1400    = extra extra large screen 

use @media rule for responsive.